                "invention-title": [
                    "Offshore wind and light hydrogen production comprehensive utilization system",
                    "一种海上风光制氢综合利用系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an offshore wind and light hydrogen production comprehensive utilization system. The system comprises a wind-solar power generation system, an electric energy storage, regulation and distribution system, a seawater drawing and filtering system, a hydrogen-alkali separation system, a gas collection and storage system and an alkali liquor sodium-magnesium separation and purification system, wherein the wind-solar power generation system is used for providing electric power for production, the electric energy storage, regulation and distribution system is used for logically judging generation and consumption of electric energy and allocating the electric energy, the seawater drawing and filtering system is used for roughly processing seawater and providing raw materials for production, and the hydrogen-alkali separation system is used for separating an alkali solution, hydrogen and chlorine from the seawater. Magnesium hydroxide, sodium hydroxide, metal sodium and oxygen are separated out by the alkali liquor sodium-magnesium separation and purification system, and generated gas is collected and stored by the gas collection and storage system. According to the reasonable utilization principle of space and resources, the prior art is integrated and innovated, and the reasonable utilization rate of seawater resources and offshore space is increased."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种海上风光制氢综合利用系统。所述系统包括风光发电系统、电能存储调节分配系统、海水汲取过滤系统、氢碱分离系统、气体收集存储系统、碱液钠镁分离提纯系统；其中，利用风光发电系统为生产提供电力，电能存储调节分配系统对电能的产生和消耗进行逻辑判断并将电能进行调配，海水汲取过滤系统对海水进行粗加工并为生产提供原材料，氢碱分离系统在海水中分离出碱溶液、氢气、氯气，碱液钠镁分离提纯系统将氢氧化镁、氢氧化钠、金属钠和氧气分离出来，气体收集存储系统将产生的气体进行收集并储存。本发明按照空间和资源的合理利用原则，整合与创新了现有技术，增强了海水资源和海上空间的合理利用率。"
                }
            ]
